// @test regression/INV073-switch-arm-leading-operator-continuation
// @description A same-line switch arm result may continue on a following leading-operator wrap line when the continuation indent is not a multiple of four. TV accepts this shape; it appears in vendor/TFlab/FVGDetectorLibrary/1.pine and previously produced a phantom Expected "=>" in switch case. See TODO #45.
// @expects parse: success
// @expects no-errors
// @expects warnings: 0
//@version=6
indicator("x")
f = input.string("Defensive")
x = switch f
    "Defensive" => (close > open)
     and (high > low)
    => true
plot(x ? 1 : 0)
